headline: How New Catalysts Are Shifting the Narrative for Delta Air Lines Stock
summary: Delta Air Lines stock has seen its fair value estimate tick up from about $71.60 to roughly $73.64 per share as analysts grow more confident in the airline's improving revenue trajectory and Q3 beat and raise. A modestly lower discount rate and slightly stronger revenue growth outlook reflect the view that recent results, upbeat Q4 guidance, and Delta's structural advantages in merchandising and product segmentation have reduced perceived risk and strengthened the long term growth narrative...

headline: American, Southwest Lead Rally Of Airline Stocks
summary: On Tuesday, U.S. airlines stocks rallied after several analysts offered rosy predictions for the industry in 2026.
